CatDescriptText: Sign reads "Teen 'O' Meter, Goal $5,000, Hazelwood youth on the move!  Help our teens help themselves put us over the top! Give now! Address donations to the Hazelwood Extension Council 4910 Second Avenue, Teen center to be established on this site. Please Help!"
TitMainTitle: Schoolchildren, some wearing "Sec. II Gladstone 65-66 Champs" patches, helping raise "Teen 'O' Meter" sign to men on ladder, Hazelwood
